description:
In this coding challenge, I create a movie recommendation engine using the a "nearest neighbor" algorithm.  In this third (and final) part, I use the K-Nearest Neighbor Machine Learning algorithm to predict ratings for movies I haven't seen yet.This video is part of session 3 of my Spring 2017 ITP "Intelligence and Learning" course.
